title: 12 Maths  Books (gnv64)
description:
Here is a collection of 12 books for maths lovers! One book is in ePUB format, rest all are PDFs. Covers are included in separate folder. All books have OCR & covers, but only some have bookmarks:

01. 1,001 Geometry Practice Problems For Dummies by Allen Ma, Amber Kuang
02. Algebra - Abstract and Concrete by Frederick M Goodman
03. Dictionary of Inequalities (2nd Ed) by Peter Bullen
94. Dude, Can You Count by Christian Constanda
05. Famous Problems of Elementary Geometry by w.w.Beman, D.E.Smith
06. Introduction to Probability by Joseph K Blitzstein & Jessica Hwang
07. Linear Algebra Done Right (3rd Ed) by Sheldon Axler
08. Mathematical Omnibus - 30 Lectures on Classic Mathematics by Dmitry Fuchs, Serge Tabachnikov
09. Mathematical Shenanigans by Metin Bektas
10. Mathematics for Physicists by Brian R. Martin
11. Maths for Chemists (2nd Ed) by Martin Cockett, Graham Doggett
12. Teach Yourself Basic Mathematics by Alan Graham
